34:06.059 --> 34:07.570
I said, “Don’t you think it is sinful
to do like this?

34:07.570 --> 34:10.139
Don’t you know as Indians that tobacco is
against religion?”

34:10.139 --> 34:12.710
He says, “We know but we don’t take.

34:12.710 --> 34:16.389
And if you give it to others [laughter], then
it’s nothing wrong."

34:16.389 --> 34:19.940
It’s like a person who owns all the race
